Package com.ptc.windchill.option.expression

Provides ExpressionService and supporting classes to work with expressions.

See: Description

    Interface Description
    BasicExpressionRenderer
    An interface defining methods for the basic expression renderer.
    ExpressionService
    A service to create/modify Expressionable and wt.option.ExpressionMemberLink objects.
    ExpressionValidator
    An interface to define a a custom validator

    Supported API: true

    Extendable: true
